;---------------------------------------------------
;
; coding
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
C00,Heating/Air Conditioning (J255) Coding
C01,0?xxx: Options
C02,+1 = Heated Front Window installed
C03,0x?xx: Compressor
C04,0 = Compressor with Clutch (N25)
C05,1 = Compressor with Regulator Valve (N280)
C06,0xx?x: Country/Market
C07,0 = Rest of World (RoW)
C08,1 = North American Region (NAR)
C09,2 = Japan (JP)
C10,0xxx?: Vehicle/Engine Type
C11,0 = Gasoline Engine with Left-Hand-Drive (LHD)
C12,1 = Gasoline Engine with Right-Hand-Drive (RHD)
C13,3 = Diesel Engine with Left-Hand-Drive (LHD)
C14,4 = Diesel Engine with Right-Hand-Drive (RHD)
;
